2026-03-02 13:26:25,263 - trading_bot.agents - WARNING - Devil's Advocate VETOED emergency trade: DO NOT PROCEED. The pre-mortem exposes three structurally independent catastrophic failure scenarios, each capable of producing 10-15%+ adverse moves within the 5-day window. The analytical framework produced a BEARISH consensus, but the Weighted Voting Result was NEUTRAL at 0.54 confidence with a near-zero weighted score of -0.019 — the system itself was barely bearish. The proposed trade confidence of 0.80 is a dangerous overstatement relative to the underlying agent consensus. Specific disqualifying factors: (1) ENTRY LOCATION: Shorting at a documented technical support cluster (280.00/278.68) with confirmed RSI/Stochastic bullish divergence is operationally indefensible regardless of macro thesis. (2) VOLATILITY COST: IV at 36.37% with forward skew favoring OTM calls means any options-based bearish structure is structurally disadvantaged from day one — we are selling into a market that explicitly prices upside disruption risk higher than downside. (3) CATALYST ASYMMETRY: The bearish thesis relies on continuation of existing trends (stocks building, prices declining) with no fresh catalyst needed. The bullish reversal thesis has THREE live catalysts that could fire simultaneously: drought escalation, BRL/producer withholding, and technical squeeze from support. Asymmetric risk favors the tail that we are short. (4) STALE CONFIRMATORY DATA: The backwardation signal (Feb 21, 9 days stale) and the self-contradiction in the Cecafé export interpretation were noted but insufficiently weighted. If backwardation has persisted or deepened in the 9-day gap, the entire bearish physical supply narrative collapses. (5) BIAS AUDIT: We succumbed to evidence-counting bias — tallying four bearish 'lines' versus three bullish 'lines' as if they were independent and equal-weighted, when in fact the bullish signals cluster around a single high-impact scenario (physical squeeze) while the bearish signals cluster around a single macro narrative (2026/27 forward supply). The 2026/27 crop is not deliverable now. The physical tightness is. If this trade is compelling at all, it belongs 60-90 days later when the bearish macro supply materializes into visible stocks. Today, the risk-reward at support, with expensive IV, in a range-bound regime, with three active bullish catalysts, does not meet minimum standards for a directional short. VERDICT: NO TRADE.
